    <item>
      <title>瑞士手表出口下滑，因对华出货量减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/swiss-watch-exports-slump-on-lower-shipments-to-china-hong-kong</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于豪华手表的需求降温，瑞士手表的月度出口量三年来第二次下降，导致对中国和香港的出货量下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/swiss-watch-exports-slump-on-lower-shipments-to-china-hong-kong</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 08:27:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>媒体报道称，越南要求 120 亿美元欺诈案中的大亨死刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/vietnam-seeks-death-for-tycoon-in-12-billion-fraud-case-media</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 VnExpress 新闻网站报道，越南检察官寻求对房地产大亨张美兰 (Truong My Lan) 判处死刑，她因贿赂政府官员、违反银行贷款规则和挪用资金而被指控犯有 120 亿美元的欺诈案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/vietnam-seeks-death-for-tycoon-in-12-billion-fraud-case-media</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 08:14:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非利率会议前通胀预期下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/south-african-inflation-expectations-dip-ahead-of-rate-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非未来两年的通胀预期下降，为央行在下周的政策会议之前提供了可喜的消息，尽管这可能不足以促使其降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/south-african-inflation-expectations-dip-ahead-of-rate-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 08:09:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本结束负利率时代，几乎没有进一步加息的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/boj-ends-massive-easing-program-with-first-rate-hike-since-2007</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行取消了全球最后一次负利率，结束了现代史上最激进的货币刺激计划，同时也表明金融状况目前将保持宽松。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/boj-ends-massive-easing-program-with-first-rate-hike-since-2007</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 03:46:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
